Run the scripts as below using user cron:

# m h  dom mon dow   command
0 0 * * 0 timeout 6h /home/hpserver/System_scripts/spotlight_downloader.sh
0 0 * * * /home/hpserver/System_scripts/bing_downloader.sh

Create a system_health_bot.env and add the credentials of the Telegram health alerts bot
TG_BOT_TOKEN="****"
TG_CHAT_ID="****"
